@startuml data_validation_mgmt_state

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> ReceiveSensorData : incoming sensor packet

ReceiveSensorData --> EnsureMQTTCompliance

EnsureMQTTCompliance --> ProtocolError : invalid MQTT format
EnsureMQTTCompliance --> SensorMonitor : protocol valid

SensorMonitor --> ValidationError : abnormal data
SensorMonitor --> StoreValidatedData : data valid

StoreValidatedData --> Idle : data stored

ProtocolError --> Idle
ValidationError --> Idle

@enduml